data.description: Welcome to this charming 2-bed, 1-bath home in Wyoming. This cozy residence features a comfortable living room, a modern kitchen with new flooring, and two generously sized bedrooms. This well-maintained home offers delightful curb appeal, and the private backyard is a peaceful retreat. Located in the desirable community of Wyoming, this home is close to amenities, schools, and parks. Don't miss the opportunity to make this adorable home yours - a perfect blend of classic charm and modern comfort. Welcome to your new haven in Wyoming!
